== Records ==
* '''Record Victory''': 6 - 1 vs [[Changchun Yatai]], QNI North Queensland Trophy, [[June 24]] [[2006]]
* '''Record Victory (A-League)''': 5 - 0 vs {{ALeague SFC}}, [[October 16]] [[2005]]
* '''Record Defeat''': 0 - 4 vs {{ALeague NUJ}}, [[January 19]] [[2007]]
* '''Record Defeat (A-League)''': 0 - 4 vs {{ALeague NUJ}}, [[January 19]] [[2007]]
* '''Undefeated Streak''': 7, [[February 4]] [[2006]] – [[October 8]] [[2006]]
* '''Most Wins in a Row''': 7, [[February 4]] [[2006]] – [[October 8]] [[2006]]
* '''Most Away Wins in a Row''': 8, [[September 10]] [[2006]] - [[December 31]] [[2006]]
* '''Longest Undefeated Away Streak''': 9, [[September 10]] [[2006]] - [[January 7]] [[2007]]
* '''Record High Attendance''': 50,333 vs {{ALeague SFC}}, [[Telstra Dome]], [[Melbourne]], [[December 8]] [[2006]]
* '''Record Low Attendance''': 10,078 vs {{ALeague NZK}}, [[Olympic Park Stadium]], [[Melbourne]], [[February 4]] [[2006]]
* '''Highest Season Average Attendance''': 27,728 - [[A-League 2006-07]]
* '''All-time Leading Goal Scorer''': [[Archie Thompson]] - 18 goals (as of [[January 28]] [[2007]])
* '''All-time Leading Appearances''': [[Danny Allsopp]] - 41 appearances (as of [[January 28]] [[2007]])
* '''Longest Period Without Conceding a Goal''': 329 minutes, [[November 3]] [[2006]] - [[November 26]] [[2006]]

